OL,3,CHeartbroken mum begs drivers not to
OL,4,Cspeed after son's death
OL,6,FA mother whose son died after the car
OL,7,Fhe was in reached 100 miles per hour
OL,8,Fbefore crashing is making a plea for
OL,9,Fdrivers not to speed.
OL,11,FJillie Slope's 24-year-old son Callum
OL,12,FChapman was a passenger in a vehicle
OL,13,Fwhich crashed into trees on the A24 in
OL,14,FHorsham in 2020, after the driver lost
OL,15,Fcontrol whilst racing another vehicle.
OL,17,FMs Slope's plea comes as it's revealed
OL,18,Fnearly half (48%) of UK police forces
OL,19,Fcaught drivers exceeding 90mph on
OL,20,F30mph roads between January 2023 and
OL,21,FAugust 2024.
