OL,3,CHeartbroken mum begs drivers not to
OL,4,Cspeed after son's death
OL,6,F"We need more police, more cameras, we
OL,7,Fneed to be going into schools teaching
OL,8,Fchildren all about the consequences of
OL,9,Fspeeding.
OL,11,F"Cars shouldn't be doing the speeds
OL,12,Fthey are doing, there should be
OL,13,Ftechnology to stop cars from speeding,
OL,14,Fthey should not be able to speed."
OL,16,FThe speeding figures were obtained by
OL,17,Fthe RAC through Freedom of Information
OL,18,Frequests to 45 police forces.
OL,20,FForty forces provided data.
