OL,4,Cspeed after son's death
OL,6,FThe RAC said they demonstrate
OL,7,F"incredibly dangerous actions" by
OL,8,Fmotorists and called on the Government
OL,9,Fto use its forthcoming road safety
OL,10,Fstrategy to tackle "avoidable
OL,11,Fcasualties" in crashes involving
OL,12,Fspeeding drivers.
OL,14,FRoads with 20mph and 30mph limits are
OL,15,Fmore likely to have a higher number of
OL,16,Fpedestrians, cyclists and other
OL,17,Fvulnerable groups, the RAC said.
