OL,3,CHeartbroken mum begs drivers not to
OL,4,Cspeed after son's death
OL,6,FRAC road safety spokesman Rod Dennis
OL,7,Fsaid: "Although this data is a
OL,8,Fsnapshot, it shines a light on the
OL,9,Fincredibly dangerous actions of a few,
OL,10,Fthat are putting law-abiding road
OL,11,Fusers at serious risk. Thankfully, the
OL,12,Fpolice were on hand to catch these
OL,13,Fdrivers.
OL,15,F"There is no place for the vastly
OL,16,Fexcessive speeds that some people are
OL,17,Fprepared to drive.
OL,19,F"Speed is the leading cause of deaths
OL,20,Fon UK roads.
