OL,4,Cspeed after son's death
OL,6,F"We look forward to the Government's
OL,7,Fforthcoming road safety strategy
OL,8,Funderstanding what can be done to
OL,9,Freduce such avoidable casualties on
OL,10,Fthe UK's roads."
OL,12,FSeparate Department for Transport
OL,13,F(DfT) statistics show 331 people died
OL,14,Fin crashes on Britain's roads in 2023
OL,15,Fin which a driver exceeding the speed
OL,16,Flimit was a contributory factor.
OL,18,FThis was at least a 10-year high and
OL,19,Frepresented 21% of all road fatalities.
