OL,4,Cspeed after son's death
OL,6,FA DfT spokesman said: "There's no
OL,7,Fexcuse for those who risk the lives of
OL,8,Fothers through speeding, and there are
OL,9,Falready tough penalties in place for
OL,10,Fdrivers who speed.
OL,12,F"While our roads are among the safest
OL,13,Fin the world, we are committed to
OL,14,Fimproving road safety, and recently
OL,15,Frelaunched our Think! campaign with a
OL,16,Ffocus on speeding, particularly on
OL,17,Frural roads."
